- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper deals with reactive systems and their synthesis. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with automated synthesis of systems. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is another possible category as the paper deals with formal specifications and synthesis of systems that satisfy them.
